\id PHM - Makua Bible Version
\h Nafilimoni
\toc1 Iwarakha i Napaolo wa Nafilimoni
\toc2 Nafilimoni
\toc3 Naf
\mt2 Iwarakha i Napaolo wa
\mt1 Nafilimoni
\imt1 Malhove o uholhelha
\ip Iwarakha ikani ya Nafilimoni yaalhepiye ni akarumiya Napaolo (nlhako wo 1:1). Ikatema yaalhepa aya, Napaolo yaari muuttukiyani, yoonihaka wiira veekinaka yaari Urumi. Paahi etu yakhalhaka yaari Urumi yeyo ikatema iyo, iyaakha yaalhempe aya yaari yo 61 baada yo uyaria wa Kuristo, ikatema yeyo yeyo yaalhempe aya yo iwarakha wa attu o Ukolosai. Yaalhempe ilha iwarakha ilha wa ntu eehaniya Filimoni, aari mmoka munlhokoni mwa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo aashunga attu ipotta. Napaolo yaalhempe wo nnikwa wo waalhepelha wiira ahintwarushe ipotta aya, Onesimo, aattawilhe ukhuma wa Nafilimoni. Wo malhehero e Irumi khalhayi vawo, Nafilimoni ahanaa ikuru yo unhukumulha Onesimo wiiviya. Napaolo anoolhumacha wo waapepecha ni waavaha nrima Nafilimoni wiira ahimpangelhe ittu yo uhilhoka Onesimo, nansho ampochereke rata thoko ntu nrumelhenlhe Kuristo nanaya. Tho yaalhepelha wiira anhiye Onesimo uyo avare ntheko vamoka ni Napaolo (nlhako wo 1:13-14).
\iot Chiri nhina.
\io1 Napaolo anowaashikuria Nafilimoni (nlhako wo 1:1-3).
\io1 Tho, Napaolo anowaalhepelha Nafilimoni wiira ampochere Onesimo thoko munnaya nrumelhenlhe Kuristo nanaya (nlhako wo 1:4-21).
\io1 Napaolo anomalhiha wo uhimiacha mathananelho aya o wetelhelha ni waavaha isalamu (nlhako wo 1:22-25).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Mii Paolo kittukiye wo nlhatu wo uvara ntheko wa Kuristo Yesu, vamoka ni munnihu Timotheo, kinoolhepa iwarakha iwe uwaninyu alhoko aka ni namitheko nkhunanihu Filimoni,
\v 2 ni wa attu anrumelhenlhe Kuristo anokumaana unupani winyu ni arokorihu Naapiya ni wa Naakipo namitheko nanihu o waatakanelha Malhove Orera.
\p 
\v 3 Kinoulhapelhelhani nnema ni mpuha ukhuma wa Nlhuku Athumwanihu ni Athithi Yesu Kuristo.
\s1 Uttuna ni upisha nrima u Nafilimoni
\p 
\v 4 Kinonshukuru Nlhuku kila ikatema vanolhapelha aka ni uwupuwelhani inyu Nafilimoni,
\v 5 ukhalhawaya kinowiiwa nrima urina inyu wo waarumelhelha Athithi Yesu ni nrima wo waattuna attu a Nlhuku.
\v 6 Kinonlhapelha Nlhuku wiira nthepeke upisha nrima inyu, mwoorie uchuwelha chinene kila ibarakha irina ihu wo ukhalha nlhoko mmoka ni Kuristo.
\v 7 Munna, uttuna winyu uhokiteelhiha ni ukihelha nrima chinene. Ukhalhawaya nhoteelhiha mirima cha attu a Nlhuku.
\s1 Napaolo anowalhepelha Nafilimoni ampochere Onesimo
\p 
\v 8 Wo yoyo nlhatu uyo etu, mii kikhalhaka munninyu wo ulhutaana ni Kuristo, kaanooria uukhanyererihani wo uhoova ittu ilheheriye inyu upanga,
\v 9 nansho wo nlhatu wo uttunani, kinoulhepelhani. Kineera chiicho inakhalhaka mii Paolo ki ntu owulhuvalha, kittukiye wo nlhatu wo uvara ntheko wa Yesu Kuristo.
\v 10 Paahi, kinoulhepelhani wiira munkaviheke mwaamwanaka Onesimo, aari mwaamwanaka wo ulhutaana ni Kuristo, kikhalhaka thoko athumwanawe vaari ihu mu uttukiyani.
\v 11 Khalhayi vawo aari ntu o uhikhulhuvelhiya uwaninyu, nansho wo ikekhiaye vano phi o ukhulhuvelhiya kuhii uwannyaka vekha ayaru nansho ni uwaninyu chiicho.
\p 
\v 12 Vano etu kinonhokolhosha tho uwaninyu waakhumme awe, ukhalhawaya vano yoyo ri thoko nrima aka.
\v 13 Kahothanana wiira athepe ukhalha ni mii uttukiye aka uno, akikaviheke mitheko cho uhimiacha Malhove Orera thoko chikenre inyu munna.
\v 14 Nansho akinookhanyererihani wiira nkikavihe uhuva waka. Urera nrima winyu ukhalheke wo uttuna winyu mwaanene.
\p 
\v 15 Veekinaka phi nlhatu etu Onesimo aari utayi ni inyu wo mahuku vakani, wiira ahokolhiaka awe okhalhanani wowo mahuku onkhaye.
\v 16 Ulha vano kahiwe ipotta tho, nansho o upwaha ipotta, vano ulha mpwana ihu. Hokiteelhiha nrima mii ni we ikekhiaye noowa uuteelhihani nrima ni inyu thoko ntu ri ipotta ni nlhoko ihu muulhutaanani ni Athithi.
\p 
\v 17 Vano etu mwachuwelhaka wiira mii ki nkavihi nkhunaninyu mu ulhutaanani ni Athithi, mumpochereke etu thoko chikenre inyu wo ukipochera mii.
\v 18 Yakhalhaka ahoupangelhani ittu yo uhilhoka ama ahowaashimani ittu, mii kinoulhivani.
\v 19 Vaa, mii Paolo kinolhepa wo moono aka kimwanene, kinoulhivani. Nansho akinowuupushani wiira ni mii nkilhiveke ukumi inyu.
\v 20 Paahi etu munna, kinoulhepelhani wiira nkipangelheke nenno nlhove nno wo nlhatu wa Athithi, nkiteelhiheke nrima thoko munninyu mu uttunanani nhina Kuristo.
\p 
\v 21 Ukhalhawaya kinoukhulhuvelhani, paahi etu vanolhepa aka ilha iwarakha ilha, kihochuwelha wiira nnoopanga chilhepenlhe aka uwaninyu chiyo, tho nnoopanga wo uthepa.
\v 22 Nansho vamoka ni yayo malhove ayo, nkaaverieke inupa yo uphiyelha, ukhalhawaya kiri muukhulhuvelhani wiira Nlhuku noopochera ulhapelha winyu mwaatti onkhaye ni mii kinoowa kooweetelhelhani wowo uwaninyu uwo.
\s1 Isalamu cho umalhihera
\p 
\v 23 Epafra ttukiye nkhunanaka wo nlhatu wo uvara ntheko wa Kuristo Yesu, nouvahani isalamu.
\v 24 Chiicho anamitheko nanaka Namako ni Naaristako ni Nadema ni ashinna Luka ni ayo anouvahani isalamu.
\p 
\v 25 Nnema wa Athithi Yesu Kuristo ukhalheke vamoka ni nrima inyu mwaatti onkhaye.
